<s> Copying a node from one document to another is quite an operation because the ownerDocument attribute of a node (or clone of a node) cannot be changed directly.  </s>
<s> Inserting a node in another document than it was created for will raise an exception according to the specification.  </s>
<s> You may have to test the type of the node using nodeType, create a new node of the given type for the other document, fill in the new node with the values from the old node, then repeat this recursively for its children before inserting it in the other document.  </s>
<s> As far as I can tell from the spec, even use of a documentFragment for copying portions of a document tree won't save you from this tedious procedure.  </s>
