<s> As has been noted before, DOM itself does not support such a method.  </s>
<s> It being a useful thing to be able to do, however, several versions of DOM support extensions which enable this.  </s>
<s> In particular if you use Sun's package, the "com.sun.xml.XmlDocument.changeNodeOwner()"  </s>
